<text top="110" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="7"><b>The President </b>(<i>interpretation from French</i>): There</text>
<text top="128" left="90" width="358" height="14" font="1">were 15 votes in favour. The draft resolution has been</text>
<text top="146" left="90" width="296" height="14" font="1">adopted unanimously as resolution 1147 (1998).</text>
<text top="182" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="1">The Security Council has thus concluded the present</text>
<text top="200" left="90" width="317" height="14" font="1">stage of its consideration of the item on its agenda.</text>
<text top="236" left="122" width="192" height="14" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 11.25 a.m.</i></text>
<text top="1084" left="821" width="8" height="14" font="1">3</text>
